title: The Voyage
description: In the last programme of the present series Dickie and family leave for the USA in a luxury liner. But smooth sailing is out of the question with a stowaway on board.

title: The Playwright
description: A scream in the night from the flat next door sends Dickie and June investigating. Since the flat is occupied by Dora Bryan, there are plenty of screams in the rest of the story too.
